OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWednesday will start cloudy in
OL,6,Fmost areas with outbreaks of rain and
OL,7,Fsome mist or fog patches. Skies will
OL,8,Fgradually brighten, especially in the
OL,9,Fnorth. However, there will still be a
OL,10,Ffew afternoon showers, and remaining
OL,11,Fmurky in the southwest.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FExtensive low cloud with
OL,14,Fdrizzle will affect southern and
OL,15,Fwestern areas overnight. Meanwhile,
OL,16,Fheavier rain spreads from Northern
OL,17,FIreland into Scotland and northern
OL,18,FEngland. Clear intervals to northeast
OL,19,Fof hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
