OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FOutbreaks of locally heavy
OL,6,Frain gradually easing in the north on
OL,7,FThursday. Hill and coastal fog with
OL,8,Fdrizzle affecting southern and western
OL,9,Fareas elsewhere. Meanwhile, hot
OL,10,Fsunshine in the southeast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
